name: Clear Firefox Settings
description: Clears different profile information based on the input parameters provided. It can delete the cookies, the cache or do a full user data removal.

inputs.description: UID of the campaign to notify the user that Firefox must be closed. Provide an empty value to avoid executing this campaign
inputs.name: ClearFirefoxSettingsCampaignId

inputs.description: UID of the campaign to notify the user that Firefox settings have been cleared and operation is completed. Provide an empty value to avoid executing this campaign
inputs.name: OperationCompletedCampaignId

inputs.description: Firefox Cache folder for each existing profile. Set it to "true" for deletion, "false" otherwise
inputs.name: Cache

inputs.description: Firefox Cookies saved on the device by websites for each existing profile. Set it to "true" for deletion, "false" otherwise
inputs.name: Cookies

inputs.description: Firefox User Data folder on the device. Set it to "true" for deletion, "false" otherwise
inputs.name: FullUserDataRemoval

outputs.description: List of cleared settings in Firefox, based on the input parameters set to true
outputs.name: FirefoxSettingsCleared

outputs.description: List of cleared settings in Firefox
outputs.name: FirefoxClearedSettings
